<translation id="6173637689840186878"><ph name="PAGE_TITLE" /> - Egon Browser Beta</translation>
<translation id="6235018212288296708">Rheol dod i mewn ar gyfer Egon Browser i ganiatáu traffig mDNS.</translation>
